description:
Game can be bought HERE
https://tamers12345.itch.io/the-prophecy-of-light-and-darkness-the-power-to-save-the-world

-----

A game where anything you desire is withing reach. Be the hero of your very own story in this grand adventure.

A game inspired by the likes of Persona 5, Undertale, and Overwatch I bring you, The Legendary Prophecy of Light and Darkness: The Power to Save the World
Story:
In a world where evil reigns supreme, one boy will rise against the odds to not only save himself and his family, but the entire world. But is a world already ruled by fear and death even worth saving anymore?
Is it wise to trust everyone you come across?
Only time will tell.
Characters:

Satan(Protagonist): A kind boy living on a farm with his siblings, mother and uncle. Almost too kind for his own good.

Bumblebee: A mysterious man with strange abilities and beautiful blonde hair. He is Satan's lover.

Tough Guy: A man fighting to save the world from the shadows.

Mindy: A woman with a hot bod who knows more than she's letting on.

Stephanie and The Man: Satan's twin siblings. 

Uncle Chip: The uncle of the triplets, Satan, Setaphnie, and The Man. He is a cruel being who rules over his family with fear.
fulltitle: The Legendary Prophecy of Light and Darkness The Power to Save the World LAUNCH TRAILER

comments.text:
I don't think this game was to the standard of quality your fans have come to expect, Tamers12345.
I was really looking forward to fighting some Robot Boys with my main man Satan, blue streak speeding on by their bitch ass, but the prologue just kept going with no action. It was like playing a VN (which if you were to make I would buy instantly because it'd be tight as shit anyway).
But it's just implied that Satan becomes this killing machine in the Freedom Fighters. It would've been more fun to see him struggle his way to the top. You'd have to come up with an excuse for why Bartleby doesn't just kill everyone though.

Overall, I give it a 8 / 10. One of the best games I ever played but not your best effort. I hope you can improve in the future. I really want to know what happens to Satan and Bumblebee!
